import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { Nav,Navbar,Container,NavDropdown,Form} from 'react-bootstrap';

const  HeaderCatalogo  = () => {
        return (  
            <Navbar>
                <Container>
                <NavDropdown title="Tipo de Contrato" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Comprar</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Alquilar</NavDropdown.Item>
                </NavDropdown>
                <NavDropdown title="Tipo de Propiedad" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Departamento</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Casa</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Local Comercial</NavDropdown.Item>
                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Oficina Comercial</NavDropdown.Item>
                </NavDropdown>
                <NavDropdown title="Ambientes" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                    <NavDropdown.Item href="#">
                    <Form className="d-flex">
                        <FormControl
                         type="search"
                         placeholder="Search"
                         className="me-2"
                         aria-label="Search"
                        />
                    </Form>
                    </NavDropdown.Item>
                </NavDropdown>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
        );
    }

 
export default HeaderCatalogo;
